{"tid":343656,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[海洋生物]淺談海星/海膽/海參","createTime":"2017-08-01T15:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T03:26:30.000Z","uid":132565,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db46db213a534bb67289921241679bc45925913a","tid":343656,"uid":132565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:36:20.000Z","msg":"今日又同大家淺淺地講下最受港男港女歡迎既海洋生物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.coolgalapagos.com/animals/Red-knobbed-starfish.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coolgalapagos.com%2Fanimals%2FRed-knobbed-starfish.jpg&h=bfbd3ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/736x/99/d4/29/99d429ae67ae3f24efccfa1adffd0d68--the-ocean-ocean-life.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F99%2Fd4%2F29%2F99d429ae67ae3f24efccfa1adffd0d68--the-ocean-ocean-life.jpg&h=0803663d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://magazine.diviac.com/content/images/2017/05/sea-urchin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmagazine.diviac.com%2Fcontent%2Fimages%2F2017%2F05%2Fsea-urchin.jpg&h=bf0891de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b1/Sea_cucumber_dish_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fb1%2FSea_cucumber_dish_2.jpg&h=c656ab68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢三種海洋生物可以歸納做Echinoderm，Echino-有刺，derm &ndash; 皮，大家可以聯想佢地做有帶刺表皮既生物。作為一隻居住係海底既生物，佢地又點得意法呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">形狀</span></span><br />\nEchinoderm最明顯既特點在於<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地係radially symmetrical</span>，睇落非常順眼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://mappingignorance.org/fx/media/2013/09/fig4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmappingignorance.org%2Ffx%2Fmedia%2F2013%2F09%2Ffig4.png&h=f60c2a2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且，echinoderms係有一個所謂&rdquo;endoskeleton&rdquo;，所以大家有時會係海邊<span style=\"color: purple;\">見到有佢地既殼，其實係佢地既骨</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sonoranresorts.mx/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/Sand-Dollar-Under-Shallow-Sea-Water-3456x2592-300x225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sonoranresorts.mx%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F09%2FSand-Dollar-Under-Shallow-Sea-Water-3456x2592-300x225.jpg&h=ffa0a82a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">刺與管足</span></span><br />\n作為echinoderm，表皮有刺其實好基本。但唔好以為佢地咁硬就無mobility，其實有好多<span style=\"color: red;\">tubefeet(管足)會伸出黎，移動佢地既身軀。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.discoveringfossils.co.uk/echinoid_tube_feet_extended.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.discoveringfossils.co.uk%2Fechinoid_tube_feet_extended.jpg&h=15d0e4dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.makeagif.com/media/1-19-2015/hPJwE6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F1-19-2015%2FhPJwE6.gif&h=11da452c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">飲食習慣</span></span><br />\n由於Echinoderms 都分左好多物種，我地要明白佢地既飲食習慣都會唔同。例如好多海參係<span style=\"color: green;\">Suspension/deposit feeder</span>，只會不停食沙／吞水，從而吸收入面既有機物。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.montereybayaquarium.org/-/m/images/animal-guide/invertebrates/johnsons-sea-cucumber.jpg?bc=white&amp;h=553&amp;mh=738&amp;mw=1312&amp;w=979&amp;usecustomfunctions=1&amp;cropx=13&amp;cropy=60\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.montereybayaquarium.org%2F-%2Fm%2Fimages%2Fanimal-guide%2Finvertebrates%2Fjohnsons-sea-cucumber.jpg%3Fbc%3Dwhite%26h%3D553%26mh%3D738%26mw%3D1312%26w%3D979%26usecustomfunctions%3D1%26cropx%3D13%26cropy%3D60&h=c43a0f99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又例如海星，<span style=\"color: purple;\">會將反自己個胃出去，係外面消化食物</span>再帶番身體內。<br />\n<br />\n大部分海膽都係&rdquo;Grazer&rdquo; ，佢地有一個結構叫 &quot;Aristotle's lantern&quot;，姐係個嘴。會<span style=\"color: green;\">刨石上面既青苔</span>，或者食海藻。<br />\n<img src=\"http://week.divebums.com/2010/May17-2010/purple-sea-urchins_walter-heim.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweek.divebums.com%2F2010%2FMay17-2010%2Fpurple-sea-urchins_walter-heim.jpg&h=5ecf0529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n非常值得留意既係，好多地方由於<span style=\"color: red;\">&rdquo;Trophic Cascade&rdquo;</span> (簡單地講就係一個因頂層捕食者數量減少而導致既連鎖較應)，海膽數量大增，結果成個kelp forest比佢地刨晒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://classconnection.s3.amazonaws.com/776/flashcards/2158776/jpg/a-142D522E6E938A1970E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fclassconnection.s3.amazonaws.com%2F776%2Fflashcards%2F2158776%2Fjpg%2Fa-142D522E6E938A1970E.jpg&h=5e72f286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Water Vascular System</span></span><br />\n呢個控制海水進出身體既system係echinoderm<span style=\"color: red;\">獨有</span>既。透過多個器官同管道，海水會進入同停留係佢地身體內，用作例如gas exchange同 distribute nutrient，再排出身體外。同時利用水壓，有D海星會利用呢個system可以控制自己既移動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.tenor.com/images/526d15d54d72531b7cef35c2d77267ad/tenor.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F526d15d54d72531b7cef35c2d77267ad%2Ftenor.gif&h=58f8d9fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">繁殖與成長</span></span><br />\nEchinoderms 既繁殖方法都有好多，例如有d海星會進行單性繁殖<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-IVuAjDGNsPs/UJsI11N-vMI/AAAAAAAADBE/vEgN87LnWXY/s1600/Linckia_multifora_comet2_PNG_PNG12-0040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-IVuAjDGNsPs%2FUJsI11N-vMI%2FAAAAAAAADBE%2FvEgN87LnWXY%2Fs1600%2FLinckia_multifora_comet2_PNG_PNG12-0040.jpg&h=6a609e6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-SRjSibmtUkI/UJsHnsM7R0I/AAAAAAAADA4/faDOm6N4jdk/s1600/Linckia_multifora_comet1_PNG_PNG12-0039.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-SRjSibmtUkI%2FUJsHnsM7R0I%2FAAAAAAAADA4%2FfaDOm6N4jdk%2Fs1600%2FLinckia_multifora_comet1_PNG_PNG12-0039.jpg&h=f8bfe47c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過最普遍既都係有性繁殖。男性女性都會將sperm同egg直接射出海水，並係茫茫大海中相遇。受精後embryo會經歷一個完全變態，流浪大海既過程，見下圖。由於呢part有涉及到成個echinoderm既evolution history，我暫時唔多講。<br />\n<img src=\"http://biophysics.sbg.ac.at/planci/images/cycle.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbiophysics.sbg.ac.at%2Fplanci%2Fimages%2Fcycle.jpg&h=f6097d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://sunny.moorparkcollege.edu/~econnolly/Echinoderms_files/image024.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsunny.moorparkcollege.edu%2F~econnolly%2FEchinoderms_files%2Fimage024.gif&h=21e1bb80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">煮法</span></span><br />\n所謂食海膽食海星其實都係食佢地既gonads，個人鐘意新鮮地成舊放係紫菜上面食。原理好似蟹子/魚春咁，識食呢就一定係成舊食，唔通逐粒逐粒食咩 <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.districtgourmet.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/HIros-Yakko-San-Sea-Urchin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtgourmet.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2010%2F09%2FHIros-Yakko-San-Sea-Urchin.jpg&h=affd270b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有唔明可以隨便問／指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45db7d89793d7ee245c976229ee52868b7c22160","tid":343656,"uid":58768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:47:06.000Z","msg":"好鍾意樓主啲學術post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩個post都係睇到繁殖嗰度就笑到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> between 可唔可以講解多啲單性繁殖嗰兩張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e3d2ba31ba81ef3b936f515bf0073d01c13c4b","tid":343656,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:53:01.000Z","msg":"海星edge of extension咪要有stem cells囉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主可唔可以講下海星既演化，點做到咁既完美星形<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8d87c3418ef340d2793c865e0d430d34e84240","tid":343656,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:54:39.000Z","msg":"夜媽媽好想食一大板海膽生殖腺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a31ae137fb8559aae5f23704d22658154cf630","tid":343656,"uid":132896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夜媽媽好想食一大板海膽生殖腺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來係生殖器官黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過真係好好食，加埋紫菜真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fceca31c4ab9a634c854639009a177f65c64e53","tid":343656,"uid":36383,"like